# pkg/database/postgres

pgxpool connection builder for `{{ .Name }}`.

`New(ctx, cfg)` accepts a `config.PostgresConfig` and returns a ready-to-use `*pgxpool.Pool`. It performs a ping on startup to fail fast on misconfiguration. Caller is responsible for calling `pool.Close()` on shutdown.

Connection values come from `config.yaml` (host, port, pool size) and `.env` (user, password, database name).
